<li><a class="newpage" href="/scp-609-ko">SCP-609-KO</a> (by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/youngguc" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1586201); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1586201&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603864286" alt="youngguc" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1586201)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/youngguc" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1586201); return false;">youngguc</a></span>)</li>
